In the manga, though, I don't think Sanosuke whips around the Zanbatou like it's a broken-off tree branch. The way it looks in the anime makes it seems as though he has no trouble holding up the sword. <br>
The animation wasn't done as well as it could, and that's the main thing that ticks me off about the anime, besides the horrible translation for the Tokyo arc.<br>
<br>
I hope alot of people will start to get into this as much as I see them getting into DBZ (I'm referring to the idiots at my school, of course.) I'm glad more people are starting to like the series, since I don't find that many RK fanatics out there. The next two episodes are the last of the crappy ones, and afterwards, it gets much better when they introduce Shinomori Aoshi and the Oniwabanshuu. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kagebu>Kagebu</A> at: 3/21/03 4:10:28 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=prismrx>PrismRX</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.freewebsitehosting.net/websites/OneWingedAngel/JackAvatar.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(3/21/03 5:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2306.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.freewebsitehosting.net/websites/OneWingedAngel/JackAvatar.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_sunglasses.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Kenshin</span><hr size=1> The massacre of the false army was just presented... ooglish.  Cheesy, that's the word, cheesy. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=chocoking>ChocoKing</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(3/21/03 6:00 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http