<img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_thumbsup.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Kenshin</span><hr size=1> I'm sure if you take a regular katana and turn it around, it would be difficult to wield it (That's probably not what you're asking, though). With a reversed-blade sword, you don't have to flip it around so it restricts Kenshin from killing people. Besides, Kenshin's specialty is battou-jutsu (drawing the sword out of the sheath and making a slash at the same instant)m so it would be impossible to perform a battou-jutsu with a regular sword without killing someone.<br>
<br>
Like PrismRX said, Kenshin sliced the Zanbatou in half by flipping the sakabatou around. Kenshin does this a few more times (I won't say when, because it would spoil things.) The reversed blade simply prevents him from killing people, though Kenshin can flip it over to the sharp side anytime he wants. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kagebu>Kagebu</A> at: 3/22/03 2:22:06 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=achohol@polykarbonbbs>achohol</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.sputnik7.com/anime/images/redhawk.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(3/22/03 2:40 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2306.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_sunglasses.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Kenshin</span><hr size=1> what is it <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=alucard1515>alucard1515</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator <img src=http://contest.polykarbon.com/badge1.gif></span><br> <font color=#336699>(3/22/03 2:58 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2306.topic&index=15>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.undeadart.com/forum/alucard.gif width=100 height=94></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_sunglasses.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Kenshin</span><hr size=1> Okay, I didn't realize the sword was 