I guess they could have taken that out when they did the english dub, but it's really kenshin's catchphrase. Besides, Iori (a little baby in the kyoto arc) even calls him &quot;gozaru&quot; as sort of a nickname because Kenshin says it all the time, and it would be hard to find some other nickname for Iori to call him. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=opaldarkness@polykarbonbbs>Opaldarkness</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(3/24/03 2:10 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2306.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_sunglasses.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re:</span><hr size=1> I like Zanbatou. It was actually created as a real sword I think, designed to cut through rider and horse, but no one could really work it properly because it was so big.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kagebu>Kagebu</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(3/25/03 3:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2306.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://liquid2k.com/datenshidojo/sano01.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_sunglasses.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Re:</span><hr size=1> Oh my god, they edited the @#%$ out of today's episode <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START |I --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/tired.gif